title: Без вины виноватая
overview: Doctor Elena Sazonova heads her own private clinic, and she recently married the clinic's lawyer, Roman. And now she seems to be absolutely happy. But one day her life changes dramatically: Elena becomes a victim of swindlers who decide to take away her successful business. She miraculously survives a car accident and comes to life in a remote village, cut off from civilization. True, Elena cannot remember anything from her past.
